snippet: The Whitney Handicap winner Cross Traffic will not run in the Breeders’ Cup Classic next month because of a minor shin injury sustained at the start of the Jockey Club Gold Cup.
abstract: Whitney Handicap winner Cross Traffic will not run in the Breeders’ Cup Classic because of a minor shin injury sustained at the start of the Jockey Club Gold Cup at Belmont Park.
lead_paragraph: The Whitney Handicap winner Cross Traffic will not run in the Breeders’ Cup Classic next month because of a minor shin injury sustained at the start of the Jockey Club Gold Cup.

headline.main: Whitney Winner Out of Breeders’ Cup Classic
